---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Why We Need This - Wasatch Back Train">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-blue-900">Why We Need This</h1>
			
			<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
				<div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Improved Transportation</h3>
						<p>A train line could provide a faster and more efficient means of transportation for people and goods between these cities.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Reduced Traffic Congestion</h3>
						<p>Building a train line could help to reduce traffic congestion on the roads.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Economic Development</h3>
						<p>A train line could potentially stimulate economic development in the region by making it easier for people and businesses to access the ski resorts, airports and more.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Cleaner Air</h3>
						<p>Utah's poisoned air is causing increased rates of stroke, dementia, and heart disease while reducing lifespan and quality of life. An electric train is one of the most efficient forms of transportation.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Improved Quality of Life</h3>
						<p>Spend less time sitting in and driving a car. Accident rates are much lower on trains.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>